snippet.description:
Another dope release on Sichtexot in early 2014: eloQuent & Warpath with their "Sense of Tumor" EP, produced by Dface (DXA), Dramadigs and Knowsum!

Buy the vinyl here:
http://www.sichtexot.com/24022014-eloquent-warpath-sense-of-tumor/ (DE)
http://www.hhv.de/shop/de/artikel/eloquent-and-warpath-sense-of-tumor-ep-353572 (DE)
http://www.vinyl-digital.com/Hip-Hop-Rap/Sense-Of-Tumor.html (DE)

SXT @ FB: https://www.facebook.com/sichtexot

eloQuent @ SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/eloquent-one

Warpath @ SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/warpath-doa

Album review (german): http://monodefekt.blogspot.de/2014/02/eine-plattenkritik-eloquent-warpath.html

Artist: Eloquent & Warpath
Album: Sense of Tumor
Release: 2014
Country: Germany
Label: Sichtexot
Format: Vinyl, 12", EP

Track A3: Heiliger Zorn
Producer: Dface
Written by eloQuent, Warpath

Mastered by Martin Glos
Artwork by Neo.Judas
